name: Learnects
tagline: Just starting to learn Python and would love a place for feedback.
body:
### ### Welcome to Learnects.
My page to showcase my struggles attempting to learn Python(and maybe some others) programming language(s), if anyone see where i can do better or feels like criticizing cause they think there smarter, please do cause im all down for learning faster(and maybe easier):

```
NHTSA.py is essentially just the national highway safety act API with the bare minimum of input and output until i get better with this whole python thing 
#Requires Python 2.7.x installed(Duh!!!)
```
